Minimal

Deprecate regular FTPS client, default to alternative.

Fixed program crashing when hitting main window Cancel button with null fields, regardless of saving settings.
Removed deprecated functions.

Save settings with .properties file by checking new Save Settings checkbox.
Settings saved when cancelling from main window.
Text fields all initialized with one function. Deprecated individual initializing functions.
Tooltips directly initialized when needed. Deprecated individual initializing functions.

Add .ico and .icns icons.
Remove external library, fetch from Maven repository.

Fix JavaDoc generation errors, generate JavaDoc.
